exportTypeUps.value.description: Choose one of the following:    * Domestic Exports  The merchandise being shipped is grown, produced or manufactured in the U.S., including imported merchandise that has been enhanced in value or changed in form.    * Foreign Exports  The merchandise being shipped has entered the U.S. and is being re-exported in the same condition.    * Foreign Military Sales  The merchandise being shipped is being sold under the Foreign Military Sales program.

saturdayDeliveryFedEx.description: Check this box if you need FedEx or deliver this shipment on a Saturday. Extra charges can occur with Saturday Service.Saturday delivery is available in the majority of U.S. cities with FedEx Priority Overnight® and FedEx 2Day® services. Call 1.800.GoFedEx (1.800.463.3339) to determine which service area your destination falls within. FedEx also offers Saturday delivery in most areas of the U.S. with FedEx SameDay® service, depending upon flight availability.
saturdayDeliveryFedEx.name: saturdayDeliveryFedEx

saturdayDeliveryUps.description: Check this box if this order will be delivered on a Saturday.Saturday deliveries can result in extra charges from UPS. For more information, visit www.ups.com.This field is only enabled if you have UPS selected as your integration carrier and are using a UPS-integrated shipping item.
saturdayDeliveryUps.name: saturdayDeliveryUps

saturdayPickupFedex.description: Check this box if you need FedEx to pick-up this shipment on a Saturday. Extra charges can occur with Saturday pickup.
saturdayPickupFedex.name: saturdayPickupFedex

sendBackupEmailFedEx.description: If this order is being shipped via FedEx Ground, you can choose to automatically receive proof of delivery when this package is delivered.If you check this box, enter the e-mail address where you would like to receive proof of delivery.
sendBackupEmailFedEx.name: sendBackupEmailFedEx

sendBackupEmailUps.description: Check this box and enter an e-mail address to send shipment notification in case messages to the above addresses are undeliverable.This message can come back to you to notify you, or it can go to a 3rd address of the recipient.Back-up notification e-mail can result in extra charges from UPS. For more information, visit www.ups.com.This field is only enabled if you are using a UPS-integrated shipping method.
sendBackupEmailUps.name: sendBackupEmailUps

sendShipNotifyEmailFedEx.description: To alert the recipient of this shipment of the expected delivery date, check this box, and enter the email address of the person who should be notified.
sendShipNotifyEmailFedEx.name: sendShipNotifyEmailFedEx

sendShipNotifyEmailUps.description: Check this box and enter an e-mail address to notify the recipient that you are shipping the package.In the field below, you can enter a second e-mail address to be copied on this notification.Multiple e-mail addresses cannot be entered in these fields. You can enter a maximum of 2 addresses, one in each field.E-mail notification can result in extra charges from UPS. For more information, visit www.ups.com.This field is only enabled if you have UPS selected as your integration carrier and are using a UPS-integrated shipping item.
sendShipNotifyEmailUps.name: sendShipNotifyEmailUps
